Markers
===========

Adding marker files to this directory will have the following effects:

force_clean_build - Will remove all previous dependencies and start installing 
                    required dependencies from scratch
                    
hot_deploy - Will prevent the apache process from being restarted during 
             build/deployment

disable_auto_scaling - Will prevent scalable applications from scaling up or down 
                       according to application load.
                       
use_composer - Will enable running composer install on each build automatically. 
               See the http://getomposer.com/
               
enable_public_server_status - Will enable server-status application path to be 
                              publicly available.
